Firmware
	•	Open ESP-IDF shell / activate ESP-IDF
	•	Build:
	•	csi_send: set-target esp32s3 → build
	•	csi_recv: set-target esp32s3 → build
	•	Flash only when board connected: idf.py -p PORT flash monitor

Processing
	•	python -m venv vital_env
	•	activate venv
	•	pip install -r processing/requirements.txt
	•	cd processing && python logger.py